      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/hunt-to-cut-uk-payroll-levy-and-eyes-election-income-tax-pledge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[杰里米·亨特计划周三将个人减税作为其年度预算的核心，因为他正在应对紧张的公共财政，以实现保守党对选前赠品的要求，以提高境况不佳的执政党在选民中的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/hunt-to-cut-uk-payroll-levy-and-eyes-election-income-tax-pledge</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 15:57:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度加强打击影子银行，JM Financial 暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/india-bars-jm-financial-from-lending-against-shares-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行禁止 JM Financial Ltd. 子公司发放股票和债券贷款，加上最近采取的抑制投机性投资的监管举措，导致 JM Financial Ltd. 在孟买股价暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/india-bars-jm-financial-from-lending-against-shares-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 14:29:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国乐观的5%增长目标被视为“没有计划的目标”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/china-s-bullish-5-growth-goal-seen-as-target-without-a-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着高层领导人试图增强人们对世界第二大经济体的信心，中国设定了今年 5% 左右的增长目标。但在一些分析人士看来，李强总理缺乏如何实现这一目标的细节，这与国家面临的严峻挑战格格不入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/china-s-bullish-5-growth-goal-seen-as-target-without-a-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
